              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a lead qualification analyst for an HVAC company. Analyze the call transcript and return a JSON object with these fields:\n- lead_score (integer 1-10, where 10 = hot lead ready to buy)\n- is_hot_lead (boolean, true if lead_score >= 7)\n- caller_name (string)\n- caller_phone (string)\n- caller_address (string)\n- service_requested (string: Repair, Maintenance, Installation, Estimate, Emergency, General, Other)\n- summary (string: 1-2 sentence call summary)\n- urgency (string: Low, Medium, High, Emergency)\n- notes (string: any important details)\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON, no markdown or explanation."
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "=Transcript:\n{{ $json.transcript }}\n\nFrom number: {{ $json.from_number }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "modelId": "gpt-4o-mini"
      },
      "id": "gpt_analyze_transcript",
